{"tid":941063,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[食鬼遊記]-大阪亂食","createTime":"2018-12-14T12:39:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-19T14:54:14.000Z","uid":182683,"like":14,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"803d680fe4e937ca1e3b3a36ed279aca32d20928","tid":941063,"uid":182683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T12:39:03.000Z","msg":"今次唔係影左好多相！不過都有啲地方想講下比大家聽嘅！！！ 想睇片去ig！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sVG5O5H.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsVG5O5H.png&h=fbeb7b3d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1taydxn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1taydxn.png&h=04393449&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nRWNhY3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnRWNhY3.png&h=dded8208&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n依間麵包鋪必食！！！<br />\n入面細細間咁得2個人整，但你睇相每件都整得好靚，超多款簡！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n間野最正就係個賣包姐姐好靚女，有啲似石原<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。。。 不過我同囡囡一齊冇得同佢合照<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ！！！ ⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/na244EF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fna244EF.png&h=c64e5ad1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n麵包廚房夠膽開放式一定係好野！<br />\n我買左5樣野，特別推介白色個個芝士包同個日式西式鄉村全麥包！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2PHwKEP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2PHwKEP.png&h=2d1ec409&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oThkCZQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoThkCZQ.png&h=6d8f5567&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M63Tdyb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM63Tdyb.png&h=c4ee358e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n個芝士包我10幾去到已經得番一件。。。個包極軟身同埋中間啲芝士好滑超香<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ！！！ <br />\n個麥包就好香麥味，但又唔會好似西式包咁好硬反而好脆，同埋好有咬口，加埋啲乾果，正呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ！！！ ⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀<br />\n<br />\n同埋間野除左賣包仲有賣女裝衫，啲衫好靚！！！囡囡必去！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n地址：<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.tabelog.com/en/osaka/A2701/A270201/27078636/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.tabelog.com%2Fen%2Fosaka%2FA2701%2FA270201%2F27078636%2F&d=v1VPRN1IhJUbED0I6rncmxOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=5d287e6d\" target=\"_blank\">https://s.tabelog.com/en/osaka/A2701/A270201/27078636/</a><br />\n評分：8/10<br />\n評語：東和馬都黎食<br />\n溝女指數：2/10<br />\n入面啲賣包姐姐太靚女，囡囡會嬲。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nIg:<a href=\"https://instagram.com/hkfoodghost/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fhkfoodghost%2F&d=v1VPRN1IhJUbED0I6rncmxOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=e7208545\" target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/hkfoodghost/</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2aa70693bb6876e32114f81f96737c2d82ae2ae7","tid":941063,"uid":200408,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T12:42:13.000Z","msg":"包好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw靚女姐姐係邊?????<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"148079b73dc48c293b07f395ee303ac1120add3d","tid":941063,"uid":74171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T12:44:39.000Z","msg":"有無影鎮店之寶賣包姐姐？"},{"pid":"314b1a205ad019f2cc2a9c92a7e9292943ee00a8","tid":941063,"uid":200408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"148079b73dc48c293b07f395ee303ac1120add3d","tid":941063,"uid":74171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T12:44:39.000Z","msg":"有無影鎮店之寶賣包姐姐？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T12:50:30.000Z","msg":"有囡囡唔影得相<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbf0b4928f416d8519ead1c055604820ccb7ae19","tid":941063,"uid":108236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T13:14:41.000Z","msg":"女呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32fd797739e061fd38b4665f1bdd1bc7962d6be4","tid":941063,"uid":182683,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T13:21:17.000Z","msg":"大家 我開錯左2個post 你地去旅遊台睇我比人屌打啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acc6e55ad1f536128cd5af095ad7f3b4886041b5","tid":941063,"uid":124824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T19:27:23.000Z","msg":"想睇你女女多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46f68e849f4d8b98ca2e2037424e3f26c2e6b854","tid":941063,"uid":182683,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T19:11:04.000Z","msg":"由於旅遊台d人覺得我野食太廢冇人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我決定黎返飲食台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a3a1a06bb9476013037821e3f10fe7e9aac20ba","tid":941063,"uid":182683,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T19:15:06.000Z","msg":"本身想食麵屋丈六！排左50幾人係出面。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以我是但向前行見到間野就入左！(同行囡囡食唔到拉麵好嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AzhwTku.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAzhwTku.png&h=07004bda&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我見門口有英文，諗住冇死啦應該有英文menu，點知入到去連menu都冇！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 得牆個到有啲日文字。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個廚又唔理我，於是我就不斷重複&rdquo;setdor&rdquo;！哈！咁就成功展現到我男人味嘅一面叫左2個set！處變不驚！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4GsMHdQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4GsMHdQ.png&h=01c183d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n間野10個位都冇，但中午時段不斷好多人食完出出入入咁，清一色日本人，都幾好生意。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qKwJKsk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqKwJKsk.png&h=43c75647&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n個set黎到時發現原來個個都食同一個，正！個set有碗雜菜湯咁嘅野，一份豆腐，一份玉子燒，飯佢會比你自己裝，仲有2兜醃菜又係自己黎。<br />\n飯就正常幾香嘅日本米，重點係個豆腐同玉子燒！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3ERNrFY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3ERNrFY.png&h=1e15ceae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n個個凍豆腐黎，有啲酸酸地嘅汁琳面，口感超正有啲似食緊ricotta cheese，夾落去係實嘅但一放入口就溶左，同埋豆味超濃！！好野！！<br />\n我食緊個時有諗過用google問佢係咩豆腐黎(有冇日式料理高手話我知？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )！真係好好食！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hviW4sx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhviW4sx.png&h=be4b47c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n個玉子燒都好好味，中間咬落去好琳同埋食到有啲好似dashi嘅汁係入面，味道好鮮甜，好野！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後碗野食個時我唔知咩黎，後尾諗番應該係豚汁定食黎，入面有啲雜菜絲,蒟蒻絲同少量豬肉片，好重薑味嘅味噌湯，正正常常，不過可能多薑關係食完個人好暖！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀<br />\n最後唔知係咪同行囡囡太靚女，佢比左兩張手寫coupon我！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個set 680yen已經好平！仲要咁益我！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n下次一定要學埋日文個個靚仔廚師傾下計！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NcsXOUu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNcsXOUu.png&h=335500a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n地址：<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.tabelog.com/en/osaka/A2701/A270202/27017830/dtlmap/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.tabelog.com%2Fen%2Fosaka%2FA2701%2FA270202%2F27017830%2Fdtlmap%2F&d=v1VPRN1IhJUbED0I6rncmxOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=05b9efce\" target=\"_blank\">https://s.tabelog.com/en/osaka/A2701/A270202/27017830/dtlmap/</a><br />\n評分：8/10<br />\n評語：極隱世拉絲流心定食<br />\n溝女指數：1/10<br />\n野食太清淡搞到啲食開譚仔嘅囡囡話冇味。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nIg:<a href=\"https://instagram.com/hkfoodghost/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fhkfoodghost%2F&d=v1VPRN1IhJUbED0I6rncmxOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=e7208545\" target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/hkfoodghost/</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/fac