ji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T23:30:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc4f1eae172b53acd1a99d8380e27fdda4fa03c3","tid":941063,"uid":182683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d3676a43225d86864c6567b8dd853750d336dbc3","tid":941063,"uid":171313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T16:07:43.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T12:12:10.000Z","msg":"多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccebb9ffaba12d36f2041890406870fd1743270d","tid":941063,"uid":182683,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T14:08:53.000Z","msg":"嘩！！依間野唔係講笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ！我每日早餐行去買盒食，我酒店行3分鐘到！！！ig有片睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X6o4B2p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX6o4B2p.png&h=6f403e21&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n間野一個人企都冇曬位，可以同靚女店員近距離接觸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，個店員幾靚女！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n入面得個玻璃櫃，有曬咁多味，買曬就得嫁啦唔駛簡！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vc2QxBp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fvc2QxBp.png&h=713f27a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nCanele最高難道係個皮點樣保持脆，我11點開鋪就去買個盒當然好脆，但有次夜少少去買個盒都係咁脆！所以我懷疑佢地每幾個鐘就焗批新嘅保持脆口！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1P2hcBV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1P2hcBV.png&h=5c889f20&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n味我唔講咁多，粒粒都咁正！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 每款唔同味同埋個面都有裝飾，唔太甜但好濃味，每款都好特別個味，有幾款係啲好傳統嘅日式口味，建議大家睇住張紙介紹黎食！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yQfeZgG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyQfeZgG.png&h=eb86dcbd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9NpfJJn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9NpfJJn.png&h=f1a6ebdf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R6HhcBJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR6HhcBJ.png&h=e74b7da0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n去日本買比囡囡一定開心死！！又靚又好味！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但唔建議買返香港做手信，因為一琳左就唔好食。<br />\n⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀<br />\n名：カヌレ堂<br />\n地址：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/s.tabelog.com/osaka/A2701/A270202/27065637/top_amp/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Famp%2Fs%2Fs.tabelog.com%2Fosaka%2FA2701%2FA270202%2F27065637%2Ftop_amp%2F&d=v1VPRN1IhJUbED0I6rncmxOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=02df80be\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/s.tabelog.com/osaka/A2701/A270202/27065637/top_amp/</a><br />\n⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀<br />\n評分：9/10<br />\n評語：我個朋友死都話係讀&rdquo;can du du&rdquo;<br />\n溝女指數：8/10<br />\n囡囡見到舊野咁黑即刻唔黑面！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nIg:<a href=\"https://instagram.com/hkfoodghost/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fhkfoodghost%2F&d=v1VPRN1IhJUbED0I6rncmxOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=e7208545\" target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/hkfoodghost/</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e772d1b3eb1421a29e13554c35446b1e9670989","tid":941063,"uid":182683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f67fb8ab25dfba407d818d22e2635cbfebb4869d","tid":941063,"uid":3167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T16:56:43.000Z","msg":"冇女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 摟屌"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T14:20:59.000Z","msg":"唔好鬧我<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0b9a833eabc76e59d20a37502ab14a2bd95aa3d","tid":941063,"uid":3167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T14:24:01.000Z","msg":"個店員幾靚女！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6f8dc59a5c6d7352108f034c02e1c380ccd9395","tid":941063,"uid":42446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T14:35:35.000Z","msg":"呢間canele真係必食<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e770fd9756d7388baf2ea6863097caa7d4f4297","tid":941063,"uid":182683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d0b9a833eabc76e59d20a37502ab14a2bd95aa3d","tid":941063,"uid":3167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T14:24:01.000Z","msg":"個店員幾靚女！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <